profile_summary:
Ameesha Arackal is a highly skilled and accomplished software developer with a strong foundation in Computer Science, holding a B.Tech degree from ICET. She has established herself as a proficient programmer with expertise in cutting-edge technologies, including C++, Python, and Jupyter Notebook. As an active contributor to the open-source community, Ameesha has demonstrated her technical capabilities through her extensive collection of 33 public repositories, showcasing her ability to drive innovative solutions and share knowledge with peers.

With a growing professional network of 13 followers, Ameesha has built a reputation as a reliable and innovative developer who delivers high-quality results. Her technical prowess, combined with her passion for collaboration and knowledge-sharing, makes her a valuable asset to any development team. As a sought-after professional, Ameesha continues to leverage her skills and expertise to drive technological advancements and contribute to the growth of the coding community.
